<shortcut><keycombo action="simul">&Ctrl;
<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></shortcut>
<guimenuitem>Load Script</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para>Executes the instructions in a file sequentially.
Nice if you want to define some libraries or something like this.</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
