<listitem><para>Saves the instructions you have typed since the session began.</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term><menuchoice>
<shortcut><keycombo action="simul">&Ctrl;
<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></shortcut>
<guimenuitem>Save Log</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para>Saves the log with all results into a file.</para></listitem>
